{"tid":160401,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唔會再笑藝讀 Ching 賣保險","createTime":"2017-03-17T16:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T06:14:53.000Z","uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3edaf9c0a9ead477ca79f35f5064a049a4ca73a","tid":160401,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"入行門檻擬提高 需大學畢業<br />\n<br />\n香港保險業聯會一般保險總會主席潘榮輝表示，保險經紀人數比5年前增加逾一倍，又指行內一直有共識冀提升專業形象，規範化及制度化現時未有監管的範圍，包括入行門檻。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前成立獨立保險業監管局，將取代保監處，接管3個自律規管機構的職能，實施法定保險中介人發牌制度，以規管保險中介人。據了解，保監局曾開會討論提高保險業的入行門檻，避免在毫無規管下，人人皆可入行，初步計劃將資歷由中學畢業提升至大學畢業，以提升全行質素，加強市民信心。據知不少保險業高層皆得知消息，故在招聘條例「加辣」前趕請人。"},{"pid":"676eb3dd3ef67a866680f1fbeac2ed534604c59f","tid":160401,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce57451529daa5cf2cc52976e5d47d932f19e17","tid":160401,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"藝毒ching賣保險份糧夠唔夠叫雞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d57a41cbb916a890c40e621546cb34a5700e94f","tid":160401,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T19:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藝毒ching賣保險份糧夠唔夠叫雞架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日放學佢就急急腳走人，搭車過灣仔"},{"pid":"21221478ed9369c132e1ecfa8d0b29b2c4a1fa8f","tid":160401,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T19:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老雞Ching ，你都係 HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef313f88976c207f5a8da34faf6b076d50fbf08c","tid":160401,"uid":36297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:51:08.000